ME</country></ep-extended-state-data></ep-extended-states></designated-states></international-convention-data></bibliographic-data><abstract mxw-id="PA128674192" lang="EN" load-source="patent-office"><p id="pa01" num="0001">The present invention provides a data transmission method and apparatus. The method includes: receiving a wireless data exchange request of a first data exchange apparatus; locally creating, according to the wireless data exchange request, a magnetic disk symbol associated with the first data exchange apparatus; and processing, through the magnetic disk symbol, data interaction between local data and data in the first data exchange apparatus corresponding to the magnetic disk symbol. By using the data transmission method and apparatus according to the present invention, wireless data transmission performed by a user between a handheld terminal and a computer is as simple and convenient as data transmission between local disks.
